com.google.enterprise.sdk.onebox
Class ModuleResult

java.lang.Object
  com.google.enterprise.sdk.onebox.ModuleResult
public class ModuleResult
extends java.lang.Object

Class representing a single result from a OneBox provider response.

Used in conjunction with the OneBoxResults.addResult() method to add a result element to the results set. Up to eight ModuleResult objects may be added to a OneBoxResults instance.

See Also:
OneBoxResults
